summary: |
    Select or provision a guest with the `System z cryptographic adapter`.

description: |
    .. code-block::

       zcrypt:
           # String, adapter requested.
           adapter: "x"
           # String, mode requested.
           mode: "y"

    .. versionadded:: 1.31

example:
  - |
    # Require a presence of CEX8C adapter in the CCA mode
    zcrypt:
        adapter: "CEX8C"
        mode: "CCA"
